---
layout: base.njk
title: "Jury of Poets — A space where poets read poets"
description: "Every poem deserves a jury. A space where poets read poets. Written, read, and curated by poets."
ogTitle: "Jury of Poets — Every poem deserves a jury."
ogDescription: "A space where poets read poets. Written, read, and curated by poets."
scrolly: true
styles: |
  .hero { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 140px 24px 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: visible; }
  .hero-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(44px, 8vw, 72px); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.08; margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0; animation: rise 0.8s ease forwards 0.1s; }
  .hero-epigraph { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(17px, 3vw, 21px); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: var(--secondary); max-width: 360px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0; animation: rise 0.8s ease forwards 0.3s; }
  .hero-ornament { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; opacity: 0; animation: rise 0.6s ease forwards 0.4s; }
  .hero-ornament span { width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--rule); }
  .hero-ornament svg { color: var(--gold-muted); }
  .float { position: absolute; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards; }
  @keyframes floatIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px) scale(0.8); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); } }
  .float-1 { top: 115px; left: 8%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 0.8s, drift1 6s ease-in-out infinite 2s; }
  .float-2 { top: 85px; right: 10%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 1s, drift2 7s ease-in-out infinite 2.2s; }
  .float-3 { bottom: 80px; left: 12%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 1.2s, drift1 5s ease-in-out infinite 2.5s; }
  .float-4 { top: 140px; right: 6%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 1.1s, drift2 6s ease-in-out infinite 2.3s; }
  .float-5 { bottom: 50px; right: 8%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 1.3s, drift2 8s ease-in-out infinite 2.6s; }
  .float-6 { top: 210px; left: 5%; animation: floatIn 1s ease forwards 1.4s, drift1 7s ease-in-out infinite 2.8s; }
  @keyframes drift1 { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-6px); } }
  @keyframes drift2 { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); } 50% { transform: translateY(-5px) rotate(4deg); } }
  @keyframes rise { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  #how-it-works { scroll-margin-top: 72px; }
  .process {
    background: #F3E8EA;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--burgundy) 8%, var(--bg));
    padding: 64px 24px 88px;
  }
  .process-label,
  .steps { max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .process-label { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; text-align: center; color: var(--burgundy); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  @media (max-width: 580px) { .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto; } }
  .process .step { text-align: center; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .process .step.visible { transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .process .step:nth-child(1).visible { transition-delay: 0s; }
  .process .step:nth-child(2).visible { transition-delay: 0.12s; }
  .process .step:nth-child(3).visible { transition-delay: 0.24s; }
  .process .step-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 19px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ink); }
  .process .step-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
  #how-it-works .scrolly-layout { padding-top: 56px; }
  .signup { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); }
  .signup-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .signup h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 36px); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .signup-desc { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.5); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .signup-form { display: flex; gap: 8px; max-width: 380px; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 480px) { .signup-form { flex-direction: column; } }
  .signup-form input { flex: 1; padding: 14px 16px; background: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.1); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--bg); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 14px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
  .signup-form input::placeholder { color: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.25); }
  .signup-form input:focus { border-color: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.25); background: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.09); }
  .signup-form button { padding: 14px 28px; background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); border: none; border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.15s, background 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; }
  .signup-form button:hover { background: var(--rose-soft); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .signup-form button:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
  .signup-note { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(251, 246, 244, 0.22); }
  .signup-success { display: none; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; animation: rise 0.5s ease; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero { padding: 110px 20px 40px; } .hero-title { margin-bottom: 20px; } .hero-epigraph { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero-ornament { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .float { display: none; }
    .process { padding: 48px 20px 64px; }
    .process-label { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .signup-inner { padding: 72px 20px; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; transition-duration: 0.01ms !important; }
    .hero-title, .hero-epigraph, .hero-ornament, .process .step, .float { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
scripts: |
  <script>
    var steps=document.querySelectorAll('.process .step');var obs=new IntersectionObserver(function(entries){entries.forEach(function(entry){if(entry.isIntersecting){entry.target.classList.add('visible');obs.unobserve(entry.target)}})},{threshold:0.2,rootMargin:'0px 0px -40px 0px'});steps.forEach(function(el){obs.observe(el)});
    var form=document.getElementById('signup-form');form.addEventListener('submit',function(e){e.preventDefault();var btn=form.querySelector('button');btn.textContent='Joining...';btn.disabled=true;fetch(form.action,{method:'POST',body:new FormData(form),headers:{'Accept':'application/json'}}).then(function(res){if(res.ok){document.getElementById('signup-form-container').style.display='none';document.getElementById('signup-success').style.display='block'}else{btn.textContent='Report for duty';btn.disabled=false}}).catch(function(){document.getElementById('signup-form-container').style.display='none';document.getElementById('signup-success').style.display='block'})});
  </script>
permalink: /index.html
---

<section class="hero">
  <svg class="float float-1" width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 8 8"><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="3" fill="var(--rose-soft)"/></svg>
  <svg class="float float-2" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 0L7.1 4.9L12 6L7.1 7.1L6 12L4.9 7.1L0 6L4.9 4.9Z" fill="var(--rule)"/></svg>
  <svg class="float float-3" width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><path d="M5 0L5.9 4.1L10 5L5.9 5.9L5 10L4.1 5.9L0 5L4.1 4.1Z" fill="var(--gold-soft)"/></svg>
  <svg class="float float-4" width="6" height="6" viewBox="0 0 6 6"><circle cx="3" cy="3" r="2.5" fill="var(--rule)"/></svg>
  <svg class="float float-5" width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><path d="M5 0L5.9 4.1L10 5L5.9 5.9L5 10L4.1 5.9L0 5L4.1 4.1Z" fill="var(--rose-soft)"/></svg>
  <svg class="float float-6" width="7" height="7" viewBox="0 0 7 7"><circle cx="3.5" cy="3.5" r="2.5" fill="var(--gold-soft)"/></svg>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Every poem<br>deserves a jury.</h1>
  <p class="hero-epigraph">A space where poets read poets.</p>
  <div class="hero-ornament"><span></span><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M5 0L5.9 4.1L10 5L5.9 5.9L5 10L4.1 5.9L0 5L4.1 4.1Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg><span></span></div>
</section>

<section id="how-it-works">
<section class="process">
  <p class="process-label">Read to be read.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><h3 class="step-title">Write</h3><p class="step-desc">Write what moves you. Any form, any voice, any subject.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><h3 class="step-title">Read</h3><p class="step-desc">Score your fellow poets. Leave the feedback you'd want to receive.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><h3 class="step-title">Curate</h3><p class="step-desc">The best-loved poems shine. Everyone gets notes to grow on.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>
{% include "how-it-works-scrolly.njk" %}
</section>

<section class="signup" id="join">
  <div class="signup-inner">
    <h2>Are you ready<br>for jury duty?</h2>
    <p class="signup-desc">Drop your email and come write with us.<br>We read yours, you read ours, and together<br>we pick the ones everyone needs to see.</p>
    <div id="signup-form-container">
      <form class="signup-form" id="signup-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xpqgbqar" method="POST">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required autocomplete="email">
        <button type="submit">Report for duty</button>
      </form>
      <p class="signup-note">No spam. Just poetry stuff.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="signup-success" id="signup-success">Welcome to the jury. ✦</p>
  </div>
</section>
